SELECT   c.c_name,   o.o_orderdate,   l.l_extendedprice FROM   tpch1g.customer c JOIN   tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE   l.l_shipdate < DATE '1998-01-01' ORDER BY   l.l_extendedprice DESC;

SELECT      n_name,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM      tpch5g.customer,      tpch5g.orders,      tpch5g.lineitem,      tpch5g.supplier,      tpch5g.nation,      tpch5g.region WHERE      c_custkey = o_custkey      AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey      AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey      AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey      AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey      AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey GROUP BY      n_name ORDER BY      revenue DESC;

SELECT   r_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch5g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch5g.region ON n_regionkey = r_regionkey GROUP BY   r_name ORDER BY   revenue DESC;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch5g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY   n_name ORDER BY   revenue DESC;

SELECT   c_nationkey,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey GROUP BY   c_nationkey ORDER BY   revenue DESC;

SELECT      n.n_name,      SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM      tpch1g.customer c JOIN      tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN      tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN      tpch1g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE      l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY      n.n_name;

SELECT   n.n_name,   SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer c JOIN   tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey WHERE   l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY   n.n_name;
